3.00	Crazy_heart	Crazy Heart	Crazy Heart is a 2009 American musical-drama film, written and directed by Scott Cooper and based on the 1987 novel of the same name by Thomas Cobb. Jeff Bridges plays a down-and-out country music singer-songwriter who tries to turn his life around after beginning a relationship with a young journalist portrayed by Maggie Gyllenhaal. Other supporting roles are played by Colin Farrell, Robert Duvall, and child actor Jack Nation. Bridges, Farrell, and Duvall also sing in the film.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5a/Crazy_heart_poster.jpg/220px-Crazy_heart_poster.jpg
